src/application/mod.rs emits TurnEvent::InterpretationContext in the primary runtime path before TurnEvent::PlannerActionSelected, so interpretation remains visible in the default action stream. The application::tests::process_prompt_assembles_interpretation_before_model_selected_initial_action regression covers that ordering.